Package: SpencerEcoTools
Title: Data Download and Preprocessing Tools for Microclimate Modeling
Version: 1.1.1
Authors@R: person("Bryan", "Spencer", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   email = "bspencer@uidaho.edu")
Description: A collection of tools for automating the download and preprocessing 
    of spatial and remote sensing data from Google Earth Engine, in preparation 
    for microclimate modeling with the microclimf package. Also includes 
    additional utility functions for ecological spatial analysis workflows. Finally,
    this packages includes preprocessing functions for nichemapper endotherm modeling.
